content: रिक्त {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} [रिच्-क्त] {@--1@} Emptied, cleared, evacuated. {@--2@} Empty, void; devoid or deprived of, without. {@--3@} Hollowed (as hands). {@--4@} Indigent. {@--5@} Divided, separated. {@--6@} Worthless, useless. {@--7@} Unloaded; see रिच्. --क्तं {@--1@} An empty space, vacuum. {@--2@} A forest, desert, wilderness.
